iavetti", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "129380083"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q15931760", "wikipedia_page_title": "Fernando Schiavetti", "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "S", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/de/articles/027948/2011-08-08"}